<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Private Candidate Shortlist | Trusted Household &amp; Childcare</title>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

    <section class="candidates-hero">
        <div class="candidates-hero-inner">
            <div class="candidates-hero-text">
                <span class="eyebrow">Trusted Household &amp; Childcare</span>
                <h1>Private Candidate Shortlist</h1>
                <p>A private, curated preview of household and childcare professionals — personally reviewed and screened, with reference checks where available.</p>
                <ul class="candidates-hero-trust">
                    <li><span class="cht-icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"></circle><path d="m8.5 12 2.5 2.5 4.5-5"></path></svg></span> Personally Reviewed</li>
                    <li><span class="cht-icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3l7 3v5c0 4.5-3 7.6-7 9-4-1.4-7-4.5-7-9V6z"></path><path d="m9 11.5 2 2 4-4"></path></svg></span> Reference Checked</li>
                    <li><span class="cht-icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="5" y="11" width="14" height="9" rx="1.5"></rect><path d="M8 11V8a4 4 0 0 1 8 0v3"></path></svg></span> Private Introductions</li>
                    <li><span class="cht-icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20s-7-4.3-7-9.5A3.5 3.5 0 0 1 12 8a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 7 2.5C19 15.7 12 20 12 20Z"></path></svg></span> Family Confidentiality</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="candidates-hero-media">
                <img class="candidates-hero-img" src="/images/candidates/candidates-hero.webp" alt="A nanny playing with a young child in a bright, elegant family home" width="312" height="256" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" decoding="async">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="protection-note">
        <p>Public profiles are intentionally limited to protect candidate privacy and respect the discretion of the families and professionals in our network. Many candidates are personally known to Diana Rose through long-standing working relationships, training, trusted recommendations, or private family connections. Some are currently working with families and are therefore not presented publicly with full CVs, direct contact details, or identifiable information.</p>
        <p>Full CVs, references, and direct introductions are shared privately and only after consultation.</p>
        <p class="protection-sub">Candidate photos are shown only where profile-use permission has been provided. Some profiles may be representative examples or currently placed professionals, shown to illustrate the level and type of household talent we review.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="fee-summary-section">
        <h2 class="fee-summary-title">Private Introduction Fee Structure</h2>
        <p class="fee-summary-lead">Our fee structure is simple and transparent — the first consultation is free, the introduction fee applies before a private interview is arranged, and the placement fee applies only after a successful placement.</p>
        <ul class="fee-summary" aria-label="Private introduction and placement fee summary">
            <li>
                <span class="fee-amount">Free</span>
                <span class="fee-label">Initial private consultation</span>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="fee-amount">AED 1,500</span>
                <span class="fee-label">Private candidate introduction &amp; interview coordination</span>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="fee-amount">AED 2,500</span>
                <span class="fee-label">Successful placement fee</span>
            </li>
            <li class="fee-total">
                <span class="fee-amount">AED 4,000</span>
                <span class="fee-label">Total private introduction &amp; placement fee</span>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="fee-agreement">Before any direct introduction, we provide a simple agreement confirming the fee structure, confidentiality expectations, and placement process.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="candidates-section">
        <div class="candidate-grid">
            <% candidates.forEach(function(c) {
                var primaryHref = c.profileType === 'real_placed' ? '/contact' : '/book';
            %>
            <article class="candidate-card">

                <div class="card-photo-area">
                    <% if (c.photoUrl) { %>
                    <img class="candidate-photo" src="<%= c.photoUrl %>" alt="<%= c.photoAlt || 'Candidate photo' %>" loading="lazy">
                    <% } else { %>
                    <div class="candidate-avatar" aria-hidden="true"><%= c.displayName.charAt(0) %></div>
                    <% } %>
                </div>

                <div class="card-identity">
                    <h3><%= c.displayName %></h3>
                    <p class="candidate-role"><%= c.role %></p>
                    <span class="candidate-status status-<%= c.profileType.replace('real_', '') %>"><%= c.statusLabel %></span>
                </div>

                <p class="card-bio"><%= c.shortBio %></p>

                <ul class="candidate-meta">
                    <li><span>Experience</span><%= typeof c.yearsExperience === 'number' ? c.yearsExperience + ' years' : c.yearsExperience %></li>
                    <li><span>Languages</span><%= c.languages.join(', ') %></li>
                    <li><span><%= c.profileType === 'real_placed' ? 'Region' : 'Availability' %></span><%= c.availabilityRegion %></li>
                </ul>

                <div class="skill-tags">
                    <% c.skills.slice(0, 5).forEach(function(s) { %><span class="tag"><%= s %></span><% }); %>
                </div>

                <ul class="protection-badges" aria-label="Privacy protections">
                    <li><span class="protect-icon">&#128274;</span> Contact details protected</li>
                    <li><span class="protect-icon">&#128196;</span> CV available after consultation</li>
                    <li><span class="protect-icon">&#9989;</span> References by request</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="candidate-actions">
                    <a href="/candidates/<%= c.slug %>" class="card-link">View profile &rarr;</a>
                    <a href="<%= primaryHref %>" class="cta-btn"><%= c.ctaLabel %></a>
                </div>

            </article>
            <% }); %>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <h2>Looking for someone specific?</h2>
        <p>Tell us about your family and we will prepare a private shortlist matched to your needs.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="cta-btn">Discuss your requirements</a>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
